name: MY CRUELTY & SILÉNT PHIL - BETWEEN US
description: I’m happy to introduce a track from my new EP with silént phil. In “Between us” my purpose was to convey a burning dynamic, a desire, a passion, a pleasure, like a love, like an incredible joy. For me this track is like a click, that wakes me up from sleep. I love very much deep house, one of my favorite tracks “How deep is your love”. I show my sweetest alter ego by “Between us”. I express my love for life by this track.
